org.js4ms.common.util.buffer.parser

Interface KeyedApplicationMessage<KeyType>

  • Type Parameters:
    KeyType - The object type used to map message types to parsers.
    All Superinterfaces:
    ApplicationMessage, Loggable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmtMembershipQueryMessage, AmtMembershipUpdateMessage, AmtMessage, AmtMulticastDataMessage, AmtRelayAdvertisementMessage, AmtRelayDiscoveryMessage, AmtRequestMessage, AmtTeardownMessage

    public interface KeyedApplicationMessage<KeyType>
extends ApplicationMessage
    Interface implemented by typed-message classes. Classes that implement this interface support a key-based lookup of a matching message parser.
    Author:
    Greg Bumgardner (gbumgard)
